oads/2024/03/Josh-Homme-Dave-Grohl-and-Matt-Helders.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Josh-Homme-Dave-Grohl-and-Matt-Helders-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Josh-Homme-Dave-Grohl-and-Matt-Helders-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Josh-Homme-Dave-Grohl-and-Matt-Helders-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Josh-Homme-Dave-Grohl-and-Matt-Helders-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Josh-Homme-Dave-Grohl-and-Matt-Helders-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/josh-homme">乔什·霍姆 (Josh Homme)</a>宣布与<a href="/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl)</a> 、马特·赫尔德斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-helders">Matt Helders</a> )、贝克 ( <a href="/artists/beck">Beck</a> ) 等人一起进行为期一晚的“乔什·霍姆与朋友”慈善演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/queens-of-the-stone-age-josh-homme-interview-times-new-roman-3556110">石器时代的女王：“我试图通过写作摆脱困境”</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">石器时代皇后乐队</a>主唱在乐队的官方社交媒体账户上分享了慈善演出的细节。 “Josh Homme &amp; Friends”活动将于 3 月 20 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的 The Belasco 举行，以支持<a href="https://www.thesweetstufffoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sweet Stuff 基金会</a>。</p><p>其他即将演出的艺人包括<a href="/artists/the-kills">The Kills</a> 、Jesse Hughes、Bill Burr、 <a href="/artists/st-vincent">St. Vincent</a> 、 <a href="/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a>鼓手 Chad Smith、Justin Willman、Sarah Silverman 等。该活动门票将于当地时间 3 月 8 日星期五上午 10 点开始发售。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fjosh-homme-tickets%2Fartist%2F2204603" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4I_33xLhPh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;